{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/learning/2018/09/11/Document-Flow-and-the-CSS-Positioning/","webpackCompilationHash":"3ea3a57f5a4a1c66cecd","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\" aria-label=\"前言 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>前言</h2>\n<p>最开始学习CSS的时候，我一度认为CSS基础很简单，但是CSS布局是一块难啃的骨头。又到后来，我去亚马逊买了畅销书<em>HTML and CSS, design and build websites</em>，书上内容浅显易懂，但是关于CSS布局，也就只有一章，而且似乎也没有提到复杂的文档流，我印象中也并不知道'BFC', 'Stacking Contexts'这些名词</p>\n<p>最近的复习中不断出现'负margin'，'BFC'，'Stacking Contexts'等等概念，又在MDN上了解到CSS <em><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Visual_formatting_model\">Visual Formatting Model</a></em>，我觉得有必要系统地梳理一遍思路</p>\n<p>本文以MDN <em><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Visual_formatting_model\">Visual Formatting Model</a></em> 这篇文章作为引导，并加入自己的理解和新增的知识点，不会涉及太多的布局真实场景，例如双飞翼布局，圣杯布局，多列等高布局等等，这里只作为基础</p>\n<h2 id=\"css标准盒子模型box-model\"><a href=\"#css%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E7%9B%92%E5%AD%90%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8Bbox-model\" aria-label=\"css标准盒子模型box model permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS标准盒子模型(Box Model)</h2>\n<p>CSS标准盒子模型是呈现每一个独立元素的基础，组合起来构成文档流</p>\n<p>以下是一个标准的盒子，由4个部分组成</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 548px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/7a43a729045b5bc22ef027fa067fcac8/2f08b/boxmodel.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.07299270072993%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"boxmodel\"\n        title=\"boxmodel\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/7a43a729045b5bc22ef027fa067fcac8/2f08b/boxmodel.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/7a43a729045b5bc22ef027fa067fcac8/0cb30/boxmodel.png 213w,\n/blog/static/7a43a729045b5bc22ef027fa067fcac8/a67b6/boxmodel.png 425w,\n/blog/static/7a43a729045b5bc22ef027fa067fcac8/2f08b/boxmodel.png 548w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 548px) 100vw, 548px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>标准盒模型我们设置<code class=\"language-text\">width</code>属性的时候，<code class=\"language-text\">width = content-width</code>，怪异盒模型<code class=\"language-text\">width = content-width + padding-width + border-width</code></p>\n<p>当我们设置背景色或者背景图片时，默认会延伸到border外围，但是Z-Ordering的顺序在border以下，也就是说，如果同时设置了<code class=\"language-text\">background</code>和<code class=\"language-text\">border</code>属性，border区域还是显示border，但是其<code class=\"language-text\">Z-Order</code>以下是<code class=\"language-text\">background</code>。我们可以使用<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/background-clip\">background-clip</a>属性改变这一默认行为，具体不再叙述</p>\n<h3 id=\"block元素和inline元素形成盒子的区别\"><a href=\"#block%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E5%92%8Cinline%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E7%9B%92%E5%AD%90%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB\" aria-label=\"block元素和inline元素形成盒子的区别 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>block元素和inline元素形成盒子的区别</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>test<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>test<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>test<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>test<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>test<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>test<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">p, a</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 40px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 468px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/63421db9665e591ddfab3316a7e1a1aa/bb106/inline-vs-block-box-model1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 107.9059829059829%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"inline vs block box model1\"\n        title=\"inline vs block box model1\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/63421db9665e591ddfab3316a7e1a1aa/bb106/inline-vs-block-box-model1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/63421db9665e591ddfab3316a7e1a1aa/0cb30/inline-vs-block-box-model1.png 213w,\n/blog/static/63421db9665e591ddfab3316a7e1a1aa/a67b6/inline-vs-block-box-model1.png 425w,\n/blog/static/63421db9665e591ddfab3316a7e1a1aa/bb106/inline-vs-block-box-model1.png 468w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 468px) 100vw, 468px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span><em>图一</em></span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 468px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/633f4bec734b64400939e0daba106f93/bb106/inline-vs-block-box-model2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 120.72649572649571%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"inline vs block box model2\"\n        title=\"inline vs block box model2\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/633f4bec734b64400939e0daba106f93/bb106/inline-vs-block-box-model2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/633f4bec734b64400939e0daba106f93/0cb30/inline-vs-block-box-model2.png 213w,\n/blog/static/633f4bec734b64400939e0daba106f93/a67b6/inline-vs-block-box-model2.png 425w,\n/blog/static/633f4bec734b64400939e0daba106f93/bb106/inline-vs-block-box-model2.png 468w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 468px) 100vw, 468px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span><em>图二</em></span></p>\n<p>仔细看上面两幅图，块级和行级元素盒子有以下几点不同</p>\n<ol>\n<li>块级元素盒子会自动占满一行，行级元素盒子不会</li>\n<li>块级元素可以设置宽高，行级元素宽高设置无效</li>\n<li>块级元素之间上下margin有折叠，行级元素设置上下margin无效，但是左右margin有效，而且不会折叠</li>\n<li>行级元素content部分出现在正常文档流中，设置上下padding会与其他元素发生重合，左右padding不会</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"css容器盒子containing-block\"><a href=\"#css%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8%E7%9B%92%E5%AD%90containing-block\" aria-label=\"css容器盒子containing block permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS容器盒子(Containing Block)</h2>\n<p>仅仅了解完每个元素自己形成的盒子模型是不够的，因为自身的盒子在某些时候还会受到容器盒子(Containing Block)的影响，例如</p>\n<ol>\n<li>基于百分比的值来设定元素盒子的<code class=\"language-text\">width</code>,<code class=\"language-text\">height</code>,<code class=\"language-text\">margin</code>,<code class=\"language-text\">padding</code>，这里需要注意，除了<code class=\"language-text\">height</code>是基于父元素盒子的<code class=\"language-text\">height</code>之外，其余三个属性都是基于父元素盒子的<code class=\"language-text\">width</code></li>\n<li>当设置为Absolute Positioning之后，基于百分比的值来设置盒子的偏移量，例如<code class=\"language-text\">top</code>,<code class=\"language-text\">left</code>等等，此时是基于父元素盒子<strong>border内侧</strong>进行定位</li>\n</ol>\n<p>关于容器盒子，我们最常认为它就是父元素的content部分，其实不然，有如下三种情况</p>\n<ol>\n<li>如果子元素position属性为默认值<code class=\"language-text\">static</code>或者是<code class=\"language-text\">relative</code>，则其Containing Block为父元素的content部分</li>\n<li>\n<p>如果子元素position属性为<code class=\"language-text\">absolute</code>，则其Containing Block为第一个position不为<code class=\"language-text\">static</code>的父元素的content+padding部分，如果都是<code class=\"language-text\">static</code>，则为Initial Containing Block</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Initial Containing Block</strong></p>\n<p>The initial containing block has the dimensions of the viewport, and is also the block that contains the <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/html\"><code class=\"language-text\">html</code></a>element. Simply put, the absolutely positioned element will be contained outside of the <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/html\"><code class=\"language-text\">html</code></a> element, and be positioned relative to the initial viewport. </p>\n<p>简而言之，就是视窗(Viewport)</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>如果子元素position属性为<code class=\"language-text\">fixed</code>，则其Containing Block为视窗(Viewport)</li>\n</ol>\n<p>知道标准盒子模型以及容器盒子模型后，需要用一定的规则将这些盒子“组装”起来，以下我们来看看“组装”方式</p>\n<h2 id=\"正常流normal-flow\"><a href=\"#%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E6%B5%81normal-flow\" aria-label=\"正常流normal flow permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>正常流(Normal Flow)</h2>\n<p>一旦盒子模型创建成功，接下来便是将这些盒子按照一定规则组装起来，默认的组装规则就是Normal Flow</p>\n<p>使用<code class=\"language-text\">position: relative</code>或者默认的<code class=\"language-text\">position: static</code>，且没有设定浮动，此时元素就是在Normal Flow中</p>\n<p>Normal Flow中，块级元素盒子垂直方向一个挨着一个，行级元素盒子水平方向一个挨着一个，一行不够之后换到下一行</p>\n<p>如果使用<code class=\"language-text\">position: relative</code>，可以将盒子基于原来的位置，通过设定<code class=\"language-text\">top</code>,<code class=\"language-text\">bottom</code>,<code class=\"language-text\">left</code>,<code class=\"language-text\">right</code>进行位移</p>\n<h2 id=\"浮动流floats\"><a href=\"#%E6%B5%AE%E5%8A%A8%E6%B5%81floats\" aria-label=\"浮动流floats permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>浮动流(Floats)</h2>\n<p>设置一个元素为浮动之后，这个元素盒子在一行中移动到最左边或者最右边，并且脱离Normal Flow</p>\n<p>浮动元素对其后面的元素或者是其父元素都会产生影响，除非其后元素使用<code class=\"language-text\">clear</code>属性清除这一影响，我之前写过一篇<a href=\"https://tianzhich.github.io/blog/learning/2018/08/22/The-Magic-of-CSS-Float-Property/\">从圣杯和双飞翼看浮动流</a>的文章，里面详细解释了浮动流的过程</p>\n<h2 id=\"绝对定位absolute-positioning\"><a href=\"#%E7%BB%9D%E5%AF%B9%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8Dabsolute-positioning\" aria-label=\"绝对定位absolute positioning permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>绝对定位(Absolute Positioning)</h2>\n<p>在Floats中，虽然盒子脱离了文档流，但是其对于之后的元素盒子或者是父元素盒子都会产生影响，除非影响被清除。但是在<em>Absolute Positioning Scheme</em>中，盒子可以说完全抽离Normal Flow，且不再对其他元素产生影响</p>\n<p>此时元素盒子的位置完全基于其容器盒子(Containing Block)，主要两种情况</p>\n<ol>\n<li>如果绝对定位使用<code class=\"language-text\">position: absolute</code>，容器盒子为第一个position不为<code class=\"language-text\">static</code>的父元素的content+padding部分</li>\n<li>如果绝对定位使用<code class=\"language-text\">position: fixed</code>，容器盒子为视窗(Viewport)</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"堆叠顺序z-ordering\"><a href=\"#%E5%A0%86%E5%8F%A0%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8Fz-ordering\" aria-label=\"堆叠顺序z ordering permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>堆叠顺序(Z-Ordering)</h2>\n<p>前面提到的都是元素应该出现在文档中的位置，但是如果发生堆叠，那么显示顺序(Z-Ordering, or Stacking Ordering)是怎么样的呢？</p>\n<h3 id=\"不使用z-index\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8z-index\" aria-label=\"不使用z index permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>不使用z-index</h3>\n<p>HTML文档默认显示给我们的是第0层，这也是<code class=\"language-text\">z-index</code>的默认值，为0</p>\n<ul>\n<li>bottom layer <em>(farthest from the observer)</em></li>\n<li>...</li>\n<li>Layer -3</li>\n<li>Layer -2</li>\n<li>Layer -1</li>\n<li>Layer 0 <em>(default rendering layer)</em></li>\n<li>Layer 1</li>\n<li>Layer 2</li>\n<li>Layer 3</li>\n<li>...</li>\n<li>top layer <em>(closest to the observer)</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p>正常的堆叠顺序，遵循如下几个规则（顺序由底向上，如果发生重叠，只有最上的元素能被用户看到）</p>\n<ol>\n<li>根元素(<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;html&gt;</code>)的<code class=\"language-text\">background</code>和<code class=\"language-text\">border</code>，在堆底</li>\n<li>没有被定位的元素(<code class=\"language-text\">position: static</code>)，根据在HTML文档出现顺序，后面出现的在堆顶</li>\n<li>被定位的元素(除了<code class=\"language-text\">static</code>)，根据在HTML文档出现顺序，后面出现的在堆顶</li>\n<li>如果使用<code class=\"language-text\">display: flex</code>，且对flex container下的子元素使用<code class=\"language-text\">order</code>属性改变顺序，也会影响到堆叠顺序，<code class=\"language-text\">order</code>最高的元素出现在堆顶</li>\n</ol>\n<p>依据上面的规则，我们看一个例子</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 500px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/617fa15eb873da38f51d397af37f6f0e/d19c0/z-ordering-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.19999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"z ordering 1\"\n        title=\"z ordering 1\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/617fa15eb873da38f51d397af37f6f0e/d19c0/z-ordering-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/617fa15eb873da38f51d397af37f6f0e/0cb30/z-ordering-1.png 213w,\n/blog/static/617fa15eb873da38f51d397af37f6f0e/a67b6/z-ordering-1.png 425w,\n/blog/static/617fa15eb873da38f51d397af37f6f0e/d19c0/z-ordering-1.png 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span>5个DIV在文档的出现顺序为1，2，3，4，5</span></p>\n<h3 id=\"使用z-index\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8z-index\" aria-label=\"使用z index permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用z-index</h3>\n<p>首先来看看<code class=\"language-text\">z-index</code>的定义</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The z-index CSS property specifies the z-order of <strong>a positioned element and its\ndescendants</strong> or <strong>flex items (children of an element with display: flex).</strong> When elements overlap,\nz-order determines which one covers the other. An element with a larger z-index\ngenerally covers an element with a lower one.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>也就是说，<code class=\"language-text\">z-index</code>只能在flex-item或者positioned-items下设置才有效，否则无效</p>\n<p>再看一个例子（在上一个例子基础上使用<code class=\"language-text\">z-index</code>）</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 500px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/9906135e95db5fe688a849591571fe56/d19c0/z-ordering-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.19999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"z ordering 2\"\n        title=\"z ordering 2\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/9906135e95db5fe688a849591571fe56/d19c0/z-ordering-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/9906135e95db5fe688a849591571fe56/0cb30/z-ordering-2.png 213w,\n/blog/static/9906135e95db5fe688a849591571fe56/a67b6/z-ordering-2.png 425w,\n/blog/static/9906135e95db5fe688a849591571fe56/d19c0/z-ordering-2.png 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span>5个DIV在文档的出现顺序为1，2，3，4，5</span></p>\n<h3 id=\"stacking-context\"><a href=\"#stacking-context\" aria-label=\"stacking context permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Stacking Context</h3>\n<p>其实我们使用<code class=\"language-text\">z-index</code>，实际上是形成了一个<em>Stacking Context</em>，不同的<em>Stacking Context</em>下的元素层叠顺序互不影响，它们之间的层叠顺序由上层元素之间的层叠顺序决定</p>\n<p>创建<em>Stacking Context</em>有如下几种常见方法</p>\n<ol>\n<li>HTML文档根元素<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;html&gt;</code>创建了默认的<em>Stacking Context</em></li>\n<li>设置了<code class=\"language-text\">position: fixed</code>或者<code class=\"language-text\">absolute</code>的元素，且<code class=\"language-text\">z-index</code>值不为默认值<code class=\"language-text\">auto</code></li>\n<li>设置了<code class=\"language-text\">display: flex</code>container下的子元素，且<code class=\"language-text\">z-index</code>值不为默认值<code class=\"language-text\">auto</code></li>\n<li>设置<code class=\"language-text\">opacity</code>值小于1的元素</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"使用z-index改变堆叠顺序\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8z-index%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%E5%A0%86%E5%8F%A0%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F\" aria-label=\"使用z index改变堆叠顺序 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用z-index改变堆叠顺序</h3>\n<p>前面提到过，<strong>不同的Stacking Context下的元素层叠顺序互不影响，它们之间的层叠顺序由上层元素之间的层叠顺序决定</strong></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">z-index</code>的initial(默认值)为<code class=\"language-text\">auto</code></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong><code class=\"language-text\">auto</code></strong></p>\n<p>The box does not establish a new local stacking context. The stack level of the generated box in the current stacking context is the same as its parent's box.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>也就是说，如果一个元素没有创建<em>Stacking Context</em>，则其顺序由父级<em>Stacking Context</em>决定，最顶层的<em>Stacking Context</em>为根元素<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;html&gt;</code>创建，其z-index值为0</p>\n<p>还是先看一个例子，下面分别是文档结构和结果图</p>\n<p>Root</p>\n<ul>\n<li>DIV #1</li>\n<li>DIV #2</li>\n<li>\n<p>DIV #3</p>\n<ul>\n<li>DIV #4</li>\n<li>DIV #5</li>\n<li>DIV #6</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 465px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/b979d63fd57c9d9c1ffd8898d1445326/925b5/z-ordering-3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 85.16129032258064%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"z ordering 3\"\n        title=\"z ordering 3\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/b979d63fd57c9d9c1ffd8898d1445326/925b5/z-ordering-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/b979d63fd57c9d9c1ffd8898d1445326/0cb30/z-ordering-3.png 213w,\n/blog/static/b979d63fd57c9d9c1ffd8898d1445326/a67b6/z-ordering-3.png 425w,\n/blog/static/b979d63fd57c9d9c1ffd8898d1445326/925b5/z-ordering-3.png 465w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 465px) 100vw, 465px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93\" aria-label=\"总结 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>总结</h2>\n<p>到这里Document Flow和CSS Formatting Model也就结束了，涵盖了基本的布局规则。只有深入理解这些基础，才能更好地去理解以前的一些布局Trick，比如双飞翼布局，圣杯布局等等，这些布局建立在这些基础上，如果理解了这些内容，自己实现一些布局Trick也不是不可能，虽然现在Flex布局已经可以解决很多问题了</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83\" aria-label=\"参考 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>参考</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Visual_formatting_model\">https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Visual_formatting_model</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/z-index\">https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/z-index</a></li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"title":"Document Flow and CSS Formatting Model","date":"September 11, 2018","excerpt":"理解基本的文档流我们就能知道HTML文档显示在Web的过程，当我们需要复杂的布局时，就不得不认真思考诸如'BFC', 'Stacking Context'等名词，了解清楚了，才能在处理布局上更加游刃有余","contents":[{"text":"前言","subContents":null},{"text":"css标准盒子模型box-model","subContents":[{"text":"block元素和inline元素形成盒子的区别"}]},{"text":"css容器盒子containing-block","subContents":null},{"text":"正常流normal-flow","subContents":null},{"text":"浮动流floats","subContents":null},{"text":"绝对定位absolute-positioning","subContents":null},{"text":"堆叠顺序z-ordering","subContents":[{"text":"不使用z-index"},{"text":"使用z-index"},{"text":"stacking-context"},{"text":"使用z-index改变堆叠顺序"}]},{"text":"总结","subContents":null},{"text":"参考","subContents":null}]}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/learning/2018/09/11/Document-Flow-and-the-CSS-Positioning/"}}}